  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Girl killed in car-train collision: 5 hospitalized",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A seven-year-old girl and a pregnant mother who were traveling in the car were killed when a train collided with a car trying to drive through the railway crossing while the warning signals were flashing at the Makuluwa Gangarama railway crossing in Galle, Galle Harbor Police said.",
        "A pregnant mother named KLS Shadila Hansi and L. A girl named Yu Dissanayake (07) is a resident of Homagama Kiriwatthuduwa area. The other injured are residents of Makuluwa area.",
        "07 relatives of several families were traveling in the car. It has been revealed in the police investigation that they were traveling in the car to attend a wedding ceremony held in Piliyandala area.",
        "The car was moving towards Makuluwa from Galle. The police said that the car drove through the railway crossing while the warning lights were on at Makuluwa Gangarama railway crossing.",
        "Even though the train is moving forward, the car will stop in the middle of the railway crossing. It has been revealed in the police investigations that the train has a bump.",
        "Three men, one woman and a small child were injured. Hospital sources say that the condition of the injured is serious."
      ],
